14 static
15 int open_gl(void) {
16  libGL = LoadLibraryA("opengl32.dll");
17  if(libGL != NULL) {
18  gladGetProcAddressPtr = (PFNWGLGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE)GetProcAddress(
19  libGL, "wglGetProcAddress");
20  return gladGetProcAddressPtr != NULL;
21  }
22 
23  return 0;
24 }
25 
26 static
27 void close_gl(void) {
28  if(libGL != NULL) {
29  FreeLibrary(libGL);
30  libGL = NULL;
31  }
32 }
33 #else
34 #include <dlfcn.h>
35 static void* libGL;
36 
37 #ifndef __APPLE__
38 typedef void* (APIENTRYP PFNGLXGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE)(const char*);
39 PFNGLXGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE gladGetProcAddressPtr;
40 #endif
41 
42 static
43 int open_gl(void) {
44 #ifdef __APPLE__
45  static const char *NAMES[] = {
46  "../Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/OpenGL",
47  "/Library/Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/OpenGL",
48  "/System/Library/Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/OpenGL",
49  "/System/Library/Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/Versions/Current/OpenGL"
50  };
51 #else
52  static const char *NAMES[] = {"libGL.so.1", "libGL.so"};
53 #endif
54 
55  unsigned int index = 0;
56  for(index = 0; index < (sizeof(NAMES) / sizeof(NAMES[0])); index++) {
57  libGL = dlopen(NAMES[index], RTLD_NOW | RTLD_GLOBAL);
58 
59  if(libGL != NULL) {
60 #ifdef __APPLE__
61  return 1;
62 #else
63  gladGetProcAddressPtr = (PFNGLXGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE)dlsym(libGL,
64  "glXGetProcAddressARB");
65  return gladGetProcAddressPtr != NULL;
66 #endif
67  }
68  }
69 
70  return 0;
71 }
72 
73 static
74 void close_gl() {
75  if(libGL != NULL) {
76  dlclose(libGL);
77  libGL = NULL;
78  }
79 }
80 #endif
81 
82 static
83 void* get_proc(const char *namez) {
84  void* result = NULL;
85  if(libGL == NULL) return NULL;
86 
87 #ifndef __APPLE__
88  if(gladGetProcAddressPtr != NULL) {
89  result = gladGetProcAddressPtr(namez);
90  }
91 #endif
92  if(result == NULL) {
93 #ifdef _WIN32
94  result = (void*)GetProcAddress(libGL, namez);
95 #else
96  result = dlsym(libGL, namez);
97 #endif
98  }
99 
100  return result;
101 }
102 
103 int gladLoadGL(void) {
104  int status = 0;
105 
106  if(open_gl()) {
107  status = gladLoadGLLoader(&get_proc);
108  close_gl();
109  }
110 
111  return status;
112 }

114 struct gladGLversionStruct GLVersion;

116 #if defined(GL_ES_VERSION_3_0) || defined(GL_VERSION_3_0)
117 #define _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION 1
118 #endif
119 
120 static int has_ext(const char *ext) {
121 #ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
122  if(GLVersion.major < 3) {
123 #endif
124  const char *extensions;
125  const char *loc;
126  const char *terminator;
127  extensions = (const char *)glGetString(GL_EXTENSIONS);
128  if(extensions == NULL || ext == NULL) {
129  return 0;
130  }
131 
132  while(1) {
133  loc = strstr(extensions, ext);
134  if(loc == NULL) {
135  return 0;
136  }
137 
138  terminator = loc + strlen(ext);
139  if((loc == extensions || *(loc - 1) == ' ') &&
140  (*terminator == ' ' || *terminator == '\0')) {
141  return 1;
142  }
143  extensions = terminator;
144  }
145 #ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
146  } else {
147  int num, index;
148 
149  glGetIntegerv(GL_NUM_EXTENSIONS, &num);
150 
151  for(index = 0; index < num; index++) {
152  const char *e = (const char*)glGetStringi(GL_EXTENSIONS, index);
153 
154  if(strcmp(e, ext) == 0) {
155  return 1;
156  }
157  }
158  }
159 #endif
160 
161  return 0;
162 }

8804 
8805 static void find_coreGL(void) {
8806 
8807  /* Thank you @elmindreda
8808  * https://github.com/elmindreda/greg/blob/master/templates/greg.c.in#L176
8809  * https://github.com/glfw/glfw/blob/master/src/context.c#L36
8810  */
8811  int i, major, minor;
8812 
8813  const char* version;
8814  const char* prefixes[] = {
8815  "OpenGL ES-CM ",
8816  "OpenGL ES-CL ",
8817  "OpenGL ES ",
8818  NULL
8819  };
8820 
8821  version = (const char*) glGetString(GL_VERSION);
8822  if (!version) return;
8823 
8824  for (i = 0; prefixes[i]; i++) {
8825  const size_t length = strlen(prefixes[i]);
8826  if (strncmp(version, prefixes[i], length) == 0) {
8827  version += length;
8828  break;
8829  }
8830  }
8831 
8832 /* PR #18 */
8833 #ifdef _MSC_VER
8834  sscanf_s(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
8835 #else
8836  sscanf(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
8837 #endif
8838 
8839  GLVersion.major = major; GLVersion.minor = minor;
8840  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_0 = (major == 1 && minor >= 0) || major > 1;
8841  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_1 = (major == 1 && minor >= 1) || major > 1;
8842  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_2 = (major == 1 && minor >= 2) || major > 1;
8843  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_3 = (major == 1 && minor >= 3) || major > 1;
8844  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_4 = (major == 1 && minor >= 4) || major > 1;
8845  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_5 = (major == 1 && minor >= 5) || major > 1;
8846  GLAD_GL_VERSION_2_0 = (major == 2 && minor >= 0) || major > 2;
8847  GLAD_GL_VERSION_2_1 = (major == 2 && minor >= 1) || major > 2;
8848  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_0 = (major == 3 && minor >= 0) || major > 3;
8849  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_1 = (major == 3 && minor >= 1) || major > 3;
8850  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_2 = (major == 3 && minor >= 2) || major > 3;
8851  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_3 = (major == 3 && minor >= 3) || major > 3;
8852  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_0 = (major == 4 && minor >= 0) || major > 4;
8853  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_1 = (major == 4 && minor >= 1) || major > 4;
8854  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_2 = (major == 4 && minor >= 2) || major > 4;
8855  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_3 = (major == 4 && minor >= 3) || major > 4;
8856  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_4 = (major == 4 && minor >= 4) || major > 4;
8857  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_5 = (major == 4 && minor >= 5) || major > 4;
8858 }
8859

10191 
10192 static void find_coreGLES2(void) {
10193 
10194  /* Thank you @elmindreda
10195  * https://github.com/elmindreda/greg/blob/master/templates/greg.c.in#L176
10196  * https://github.com/glfw/glfw/blob/master/src/context.c#L36
10197  */
10198  int i, major, minor;
10199 
10200  const char* version;
10201  const char* prefixes[] = {
10202  "OpenGL ES-CM ",
10203  "OpenGL ES-CL ",
10204  "OpenGL ES ",
10205  NULL
10206  };
10207 
10208  version = (const char*) glGetString(GL_VERSION);
10209  if (!version) return;
10210 
10211  for (i = 0; prefixes[i]; i++) {
10212  const size_t length = strlen(prefixes[i]);
10213  if (strncmp(version, prefixes[i], length) == 0) {
10214  version += length;
10215  break;
10216  }
10217  }
10218 
10219 /* PR #18 */
10220 #ifdef _MSC_VER
10221  sscanf_s(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
10222 #else
10223  sscanf(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
10224 #endif
10225 
10226  GLVersion.major = major; GLVersion.minor = minor;
10227  GLAD_GL_ES_VERSION_2_0 = (major == 2 && minor >= 0) || major > 2;
10228  GLAD_GL_ES_VERSION_3_0 = (major == 3 && minor >= 0) || major > 3;
10229  GLAD_GL_ES_VERSION_3_1 = (major == 3 && minor >= 1) || major > 3;
10230 }
10231 
10232 int gladLoadGLES2Loader(GLADloadproc load) {
10233  GLVersion.major = 0; GLVersion.minor = 0;
10234  glGetString = (PFNGLGETSTRINGPROC)load("glGetString");
10235  if(glGetString == NULL) return 0;
10236  if(glGetString(GL_VERSION) == NULL) return 0;
10237  find_coreGLES2();
10238  load_GL_ES_VERSION_2_0(load);
10239  load_GL_ES_VERSION_3_0(load);

10722 static void find_coreGLES1(void) {
10723 
10724  /* Thank you @elmindreda
10725  * https://github.com/elmindreda/greg/blob/master/templates/greg.c.in#L176
10726  * https://github.com/glfw/glfw/blob/master/src/context.c#L36
10727  */
10728  int i, major, minor;
10729 
10730  const char* version;
10731  const char* prefixes[] = {
10732  "OpenGL ES-CM ",
10733  "OpenGL ES-CL ",
10734  "OpenGL ES ",
10735  NULL
10736  };
10737 
10738  version = (const char*) glGetString(GL_VERSION);
10739  if (!version) return;
10740 
10741  for (i = 0; prefixes[i]; i++) {
10742  const size_t length = strlen(prefixes[i]);
10743  if (strncmp(version, prefixes[i], length) == 0) {
10744  version += length;
10745  break;
10746  }
10747  }
10748 
10749 /* PR #18 */
10750 #ifdef _MSC_VER
10751  sscanf_s(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
10752 #else
10753  sscanf(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
10754 #endif
10755 
10756  GLVersion.major = major; GLVersion.minor = minor;
10757  GLAD_GL_VERSION_ES_CM_1_0 = (major == 1 && minor >= 0) || major > 1;
10758 }
10759 
10760 int gladLoadGLES1Loader(GLADloadproc load) {
10761  GLVersion.major = 0; GLVersion.minor = 0;
10762  glGetString = (PFNGLGETSTRINGPROC)load("glGetString");
10763  if(glGetString == NULL) return 0;
10764  if(glGetString(GL_VERSION) == NULL) return 0;
10765  find_coreGLES1();
10766  load_GL_VERSION_ES_CM_1_0(load);
10767 
10768  find_extensionsGLES1();
